Info - 
India's first hilarious hindi comedy made especially for youtube audience. It has been made on a shoe string budget . Even though we have no item song or stars , the audience viewership & support for the film has been great.

.The film is a senseless comedy leading to senseless situations. If you enjoy situational comedies or old comedies of Hrishikesh mukherji or more recently 3 idiots, you should enjoy this film.

The film can be classified as a situational comedy. It has been inspired by american television shows , mainly seinfeld & friends but has an original storyline. The funny film was shot in Mumbai.

As the film is made for youtube audience , we are looking forward to your feedback & comments on the film. Its not a typical bollywood movie but for you tube online viewers for year 2013. Its an Independently made Indian film for youtube

This recent hindi movie released in 2013 starts Abhishek Patel, Siddharth Tewatiya, Afshad Kelawala, Shinjini Rawal, Elena Kazan , Nayani Dixit
